      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="262.txt-7">
      <text>Phyllaries 25–35+ in 4–5+ series, glabrescent, margins arachno-ciliolate, the outer lance-ovate, 1–3 mm, inner oblong to linear-oblong, 5–7+ mm, tips acute or rounded-apiculate.</text>
